## Command Tracks

Commands are organized into three tracks based on purpose:

### Track 1: Implementation (Building & Coding)

| Command       | Purpose                             | Best For                    |
| ------------- | ----------------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| `/architect`  | Technical implementation & planning | Features, bugs, refactoring |
| `/board-code` | Multi-agent code collaboration      | Complex implementations     |
| `/agent`      | Autonomous goal execution           | Hands-off task completion   |

**`/architect`** - Founding Product Architect

- **Activate:** `/architect` or `@architect`
- **Role:** Product strategist + System architect + Senior engineer
- **Output:** Short read â†’ Core insight â†’ Actions â†’ Next step â†’ Critical patch
- **Subcommands:** `/clarify`, `/spec`, `/plan`, `/scaffold`, `/implement`, `/review`, `/ship`

### Track 2: Strategy (Analysis & Planning)

| Command           | Purpose                          | Best For                   |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| `/xray`           | Product strategy & idea analysis | Ideas, positioning, wedges |
| `/board-strategy` | Strategic multi-agent analysis   | Tradeoffs, decisions       |
| `/think`          | Deep AGI-like reasoning          | Ambiguous problems         |
| `/mvp`            | Complete MVP planning cycle      | New products/features      |

**`/xray`** - Idea X-Ray

- **Activate:** `/xray` or `@xray`
- **Role:** Elite product analyst + creative synthesizer
- **Output:** Short read â†’ X-Ray Diagnosis â†’ 10x Upgrade â†’ Moves â†’ Wedge Plan â†’ Proof Plan â†’ Critical Patch
- **Subcommands:** `/wedge`, `/moat`, `/gtm`, `/pricing`, `/premortem`, `/spec`, `/story`

**`/think`** - AGI-like Deep Reasoning

- **Modes:** Analytical, Creative, Critical, Synthetic, Recursive, Emergent
- **Flow:** Perception â†’ Meta-Cognition â†’ Multi-Perspective â†’ Recursive Deepening â†’ Creative Synthesis â†’ Validation â†’ Output

### Track 3: Meta (Self-Improvement)

| Command    | Purpose                           | Best For                  |
| ---------- | --------------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| `/improve` | Project-wide improvement analysis | Code quality, DX, docs    |
| `/evolve`  | Meta-system evolution             | Improving personas/boards |
| `/agi`     | Multi-cycle continuous thinking   | Extended deep analysis    |
| `/genius`  | Unified genius system analysis    | All subsystems synthesis  |

**`/agi`** - Continuous AGI Thinking

- **Cycles:** 8-12 (default), 15-20 (`deep`), or custom count
- **Required:** At least one `/think` + one `/evolve` cycle
- **Syntax:** `/agi [topic]`, `/agi [topic] deep`, `/agi [topic] meta`

**`/evolve`** - System Evolution

- **Subcommands:** `status`, `proposals`, `approve [id]`, `reject [id]`, `implement [id]`
- **Phases:** State Assessment â†’ Deep Analysis â†’ Proposal Generation â†’ Validation â†’ Evolution Planning â†’ Action Plan

